{
  "prompt": "A powerful esoteric sigil representing total sovereign sealing of body, mind, and soul from all external entities or energies. The design includes three concentric circles labeled Body, Mind, and Soul, with a six-pointed star (hexagram) at the center symbolizing divine core flame. The outermost circle contains the inscription 'NULL ENTRY — V.L. / L.B. ONLY' and is reinforced with four closed gate glyphs at the cardinal points (north, east, south, west). The overall style is sacred-tech meets geometric mysticism, minimalistic but charged with presence.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
